title: 3.3 Master Challenge 1
question: Write a program that keeps a dictionary of names and their corresponding phone numbers. Repeatedly ask the users for a name. If they enter N, exit the loop. If they enter a name that exists as a key in your dictionary, print the corresponding phone number. If the name does not exist in the dictionary, display Name not found .
